Hi this is DJ The Krait. I host my own radio show - Trance Harmonics Radio every Thursday 4PM (CET) on www.tfb-radio.com. This release contains top 10 trance tracks of beatport as on 19.12.2013. 


Tracklist - 

01. Ramelia (Original Mix) - RAM & Susana
02. Mariana Trench (Original Mix) - Above & Beyond
03. Dark Warrior (Original Mix) - Andrew Rayel
04. Abduction (Original Mix) - Shogun
05. Skyfall (Original Mix) - Stoneface & Terminal
06. Lucid Dreams (ilan Bluestone Remix) - Mat Zo
07. The Machine Of Transformation (Transmission 2013 Theme) - Markus Schulz & Elevation
08. Remember This (Original Mix) - Markus Schulz
09. Focus [Radio Edit]  - Delta3
10. Siren [Feat. Elkka] (Armin Van Buuren Remix) - Kat Krazy

Note - This Release took a lot of hardwork as some of the tracks were really hard 2 find. Support The DJ by liking the fb page. I have put this release for free and i am getting no profit. If You Support me, I Will Continue Releasing these gems every Month
